        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1954-02-17T19:32:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1954-02-17T19:32:00-05:00" n="100"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d100">
                <head>100. Telegram From <gloss type="from">Operation <gloss
                            target="#t_PBSPBSUCCESS1">PBSUCCESS</gloss> Headquarters in
                        Florida</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Central Intelligence Agency</gloss>
                    <note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d100fn1">Source: Central Intelligence Agency,
                        Job 79-01025A, Box 1, Folder 6. Secret; Routine; RYBAT; <gloss
                            target="#t_PBSPBSUCCESS1">PBSUCCESS</gloss>. Repeated to Guatemala
                        City.</note>
                </head>
                <dateline>[<hi rend="italic">place not declassified</hi>], <date
                        calendar="gregorian" when="1954-02-18T00:32:00+00:00">February 18, 1954,
                        0032Z</date>.</dateline>
                <p>579. 1. Suggest one shot <gloss target="#t_KUGOWN1">KUGOWN</gloss> operation to
                    effect rapid distribution propaganda <gloss target="#t_WSBURNT1">WSBURNT</gloss>
                    Church circles, continuing during <gloss target="#t_PBSPBSUCCESS1"
                        >PBSUCCESS</gloss>.</p>
                <p>2. Assuming [<hi rend="italic">less than 1 line of source text not
                        declassified</hi>] still available [<hi rend="italic">less than 1 line of
                        source text not declassified</hi>], suggest he be sent two week visit <gloss
                        target="#t_WSBURNT1">WSBURNT</gloss> bearing letter introduction to MSGR
                        <persName>Rossell Arellano</persName>.</p>
                <p>3. At Guat’s discretion [<hi rend="italic">less than 1 line of source text not
                        declassified</hi>] would reveal intentions to <persName>Rossell</persName>,
                    or would work directly through persons like [<hi rend="italic">2 names not
                        declassified</hi>] ([<hi rend="italic">document indicator not
                        declassified</hi>]–1438) and [<hi rend="italic">name not declassified</hi>]
                        ([<hi rend="italic">document indicator not declassified</hi>]-649).</p>
                <p>4. [<hi rend="italic">less than 1 line of source text not declassified</hi>]
                    would carry to <gloss target="#t_WSBURNT1">WSBURNT</gloss> basic material for
                    producing several series pamphlets and posters; also funds paying local
                    creative, production, distribution services.</p>
                <p>5. Estimate that above program would be effective despite lack usual controls,
                    owing Church motivation and rapport within clergy. Proposal has additional merit
                    if carried out immediately; vis, that of assessing <gloss
                        target="#t_PBSPBSUCCESS1">PBSUCCESS</gloss> assets within clergy.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
